            <thetext>Now all tests must be bundled into one application. This is a problem since low level tests must be performed within the same application/HTML-page as widget tests. Further it is not possible to have different compiler settings for different tests.

JSUnit can handle test suites with tests from different HMTL files. We should support something similar. Maybe we can take some code from the demo browser, which already has separate applications for each demo.</thetext>
